==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Publisher
<hw>Pub"lish*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who publishes;
<as>as, a <ex>publisher</ex> of a book or magazine</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>For love of you, not hate unto my friend,⟦br⟧
Hath made me <qex>publisher</qex> of this pretense.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Publishment</ent>⟦br⟧
